Univariate time series models: Simulations 
Parameters :
mu = 6;          
phi = 0.9;       
sigma2 = 3;      
sigma = sqrt(sigma2);
T = 500;  
y = zeros(T,1);

y(1) = mu;

e = sigma * randn(T,1); 
Process:
for t = 2:T
    y(t) = mu + phi*(y(t-1) - mu) + e(t);
end
Plot:
figure;
plot(y, 'LineWidth', 1.2);
xlabel('Time');
ylabel('y_t');
title('Simulated AR(1) Process');
grid on;
